# User Uploaded Images Directory

This directory stores images uploaded by users through the admin interface.

## Usage
- User-uploaded product images and category images
- Processed and optimized by the image upload system
- Automatic compression and resizing applied
- Served via API endpoints with proper caching headers

## Features
- Automatic image optimization (60% compression)
- Support for PNG, JPG, GIF, WebP formats
- Drag & drop upload interface
- Gallery management system
- Thumbnail generation

## API Access
- Upload: POST /api/upload
- Gallery: GET /api/images
- Delete: DELETE /api/images/:filename
